                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">Consultez et gérez votre inventaire de médicaments, surveillez les niveaux de stock et configurez des alertes.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <a href="{{ path('app_pharma_stock') }}" class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-500 dark:hover:text-blue-300 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                            Gérer le stock
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <span class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">Essentiel</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Prescriptions Card -->
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-lg dark:shadow-gray-900 dark:hover:shadow-gray-800 transition-all duration-300 group border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
                <div class="bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20 p-6">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Ordonnances</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">Consultez et traitez les ordonnances des patients, vérifiez les médicaments prescrits et leur disponibilité.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <a href="{{ path('app_pharma_ordonnance') }}" class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-500 dark:hover:text-indigo-300 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                            Traiter les ordonnances
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <span class="bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/40 text-indigo-800 dark:text-indigo-300 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">15 en attente</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Profile Card -->
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-lg dark:shadow-gray-900 dark:hover:shadow-gray-800 transition-all duration-300 group border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
                <div class="bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 p-6">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Profil & Paramètres</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">Gérez vos informations personnelles, modifiez les paramètres du compte et configurez les préférences.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <a href="{{ path('app_pharma_profil') }}" class="inline-flex items-center font-medium text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-500 dark:hover:text-purple-300 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300">
                            Modifier le profil
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <span class="bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/40 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-300 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">À jour</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Recent Activity -->
